messages.content: Rodophis leads Dulci here. “Well, here we are.”
She seemed amazed "Woah...."
“Isnt it great?”
She nodded
“C’mon, let’s see what they have.”
"Ok~!" She smiled at her
She stepped inside, seeing a surprising variety.
“...Y’know what’s great about sharing a mind? Hearing your thoughts.” She whispered.
She blushed a bit "Yeah...~"
“Your thoughts are sweet...” she said, kissing her cheek. “Just like you, Princess.”
She blushed more, giggling a bit
She laughed. “What, you thought I didn’t remember?”
"Well its the same for you my dear knight~"
“You’re so much stronger than I thought you were... having to look despair in the face not once, but twice...”
She froze a bit "....I....killed in one....I dont know how strong that makes me..."
“Yes, but you survived the other.” She placed a hand on her shoulder.
"I-I dont wanna...think about it...."
“All right then, let’s not.”
She clutched her hand tightly
“Shh, Shh...” she rubbed her back. “It’s OK, they can’t get you here.”
She just hugged her tightly
She hugged her back.
“I’m...sorry.”
"I-its ok...." She smiled "Ill be fine..."
“I know you will...” she said, keeping her hands intertwined.
She smooched her forehead
She laughed, tail wagging.
She giggled, smooching her again
@Gekitoutsu Rispba
“Now come on, let’s get some ice cream.”

She kept her tail wrapped as well.

The bell attached to the door jingles as Repluis walked in....,sure he could’ve done so many things right now but......he never tasted....sweets.....before..
in the mindscape all that he tasted was smoke and the tanginess of blood..... 
*hey, goop....you there?*
_We are here._ The goop responded _Those 2 girls over there. They are part of the hive mind. Just thought you should know. They will leave you alone most likely._
*oh, really?*. He turned his head to snatch a glance at them, huh. Before looking back at the glass revealing an array of colorful flavors. *can you....taste?*. His eyes widen in glee
_Hm....We....think so....Yes. yes we can taste. Why do you ask?_
*pick a flavor that interests you, it’s....my first time trying ice cream...and I was wondering if it was yours too.*
The goop seemed excited _Oo..._ it looks over the flavors and decides on one _Cookies and cream....it sounds good...._

*gotcha,*. He eagerly points to the section and asks the server for one....*no two*! Two scoops of cookies and cream... soon enough the heavenly treat was placed on a cone and handed to him, *we...gotta pay for this...right..?*. Where in the Void...does Sanguis put his munny?
The goop had no idea what munny was...

There it is...perhaps is was too much but it technically wasn’t his munny *sooo*. He slaps the amount on the counter, not bothering to take change, Repluis walks outside and leans against the window. Taking the first lick...,and oh boy was it the most heavenly he ever experienced. “W-Woah...” there was even little pieces of cookie dough in it!
_Woah.....Its...wow...We have.....never had ice cream before....or any kind of food..._ The goop was enjoying the flavor
Dulci looked back at him, brow furrowed a bit. Why....does he seem so familiar....
*I know right?! I can’t believe what we missed out on! So much flavor!* he happily takes another lick, not paying attention to the staring behind him.

The goop is happy. Very happy!

Meanwhile a certain Tanuki passes by the store, humming to herself

He was very much enjoying himself with the company of his new friend 
Until that tanuki passed by, for some reason...a shiver passed up his spine....*yikes....was it just me, or did that lady give us the heebidy jeebies....yucks*
_We felt it.....Definitely bad vibes from her...._ The goop shivered a bit _We have a question. Who is this Vulpe we see in the memories? She is interesting...._
*Huh? Vulpe? Oh yeah......uhm...someone Who’s dating Sanguis.....I’d like to thing we share her....but yeah, she is a really interesting mun...*
The goop hummed a bit _What is.....dating?_
*uhm.....I think...it’s when two muns love each other and they.....uh....do romance with each other....*
_Interesting....._ It hummed _It sounds like a nice feeling..._

*yeah....I felt a weird feeling when I saw Vulpe.....it was a very nice feeling.....felt warm and fuzzy...* he gives a reminiscent sigh, *I wish I was able to feel it more, it made me feel whole for once.*
_Hm....Maybe now that youre in control you can find her?_ The goop suggested
*right! But......she might get suspicious.....*
_Hmm....Well maybe we can help you act like Sanguis?_
*really? Hmmm, yeah! Maybe that would work!*
_Just let us know when and we will help._ The goop hummed
*much thanks!*, easily finishing off the cone, he stretches a bit then starts to walk away....now...where to find his **kitty**?
“Did that boy seem...familiar to you?” Rodophis asked, watching Repilius while eating her ice cream.
"Yeah.... He did......I dont know why..."
“Me neither...” Rodo said softly, before shrugging it off.
“Your sister...she’s very kind. She’s the first one who truly understood us...”
"Yes....Dulcis sister...Aion...Very nice. Shale is good too!"
“She is...” Rodo nodded. “I’m glad we found her.”

".....You heard that right? We must scatter...."
@Gekitoutsu Rispba
“Yeah.” Rodophis nodded, giving her one last kiss.
"Ill miss being able to kiss you......" She hummed, leaning into the kiss
“Me too, but we have to stay safe.”
She nodded "I hope I can see you again soon my love...."
“Same to you...princess.” She said, before leaving.
